com.yworks.yfiles.view.input

Interface IBendSnapResultProvider


  • public interface IBendSnapResultProvider
    Interface that is used by the GraphSnapContext for bends to collect a number of SnapResults during the move/edit operation.

    This interface is queried from the ILookup of the IBends that are being moved during the edit.

    See Also:
    GraphSnapContext, BendDecorator.getBendSnapResultProviderDecorator()

      • collectSnapResults

        void collectSnapResults(GraphSnapContext context,
                        CollectSnapResultsEventArgs args,
                        PointD suggestedLocation,
                        IBend bend)
        Called when a node is dragged to add SnapResults for OrthogonalSnapLines to which this bend can potentially snap.
        Parameters:
        context - The snap context which manages the snap lines and the settings.
        args - The event argument to obtain the necessary information from and add results to.
        suggestedLocation - The location of the bend if the bend would not snap.
        bend - The bend that is being moved.
